elements.2211.03185_d2bf4d276140566908eeca313a5cf: Although the anomalous Hall effect (AHE) has been discovered experimentally in 1881
elements.2211.03185_29cb0e6ae180c20be08f739e1a1aa: , understanding its microscopic origins took longer to come, and its connection to topological properties of the electronic band structure has only been recently realized
elements.2211.03185_16af4f9319e8eb1339b2d91c8f948: Much of the attention has been focused on materials with strong spin-orbit interaction
elements.2211.03185_8e15d30b5fb8b485f135d6560cbb2: In this case, several mechanisms contribute to the AHE
elements.2211.03185_044701e3c812b322dafd3ca88bbae: These mechanisms can be divided into intrinsic and extrinsic mechanisms
elements.2211.03185_138fbab40d9a76ed304127131c290: The intrinsic contribution depends solely on the band structure of the material, and its origin is the anomalous velocity of the electrons due to their Berry curvature
elements.2211.03185_1778d504cd270aa30421b75521af7: The extrinsic contribution involves scattering of electrons, and semiclassicaly it can be separated to the skew-scattering and side-jump mechanisms
elements.2211.03185_955424923ec8b0ee1b2f33586dfad: These competing mechanisms give rise to the complexity of the AHE
elements.2211.03185_6f7c86793d1f7d1c10d025f4f00a8: The magnitudes of the different processes scale differently with carrier density and the nature of the disorder, making the behavior of the AHE rich and complex.
elements.2211.03185_9d705a0a7684131e34765dc1e7305: In this work we focus on the problem of AHE in Weyl semimetals (WSMs) with broken time-reversal symmetry (TRS)
elements.2211.03185_746282f92226248a73e530cf8b2b9: WSMs have a strong spin-orbit interaction necessary for the AHE, and moreover the Weyl nodes are sources of Berry curvature
elements.2211.03185_7394e45b8f380f2f00597c78bde0b: When the chemical potential is in the vicinity of the Weyl nodes, the intrinsic mechanism dominates the AHE, giving rise to the pseudo-quantized AHE conductivity
elements.2211.03185_b58ef1523c9b762da0bd4536dc7f9: However, away from that point, Fermi surfaces are formed around Weyl nodes and the extrinsic mechanisms contribute as well
elements.2211.03185_a4a678f28ed3899ff7c0005706ece: The relative role of intrinsic and extrinsic processes for different spectrum was studied experimentally for the WSMs PrAlGe
elements.2211.03185_af8f996a2735344e1df8da66245de: By continuously varying the doping, the relative importance of the extrinsic and intrinsic mechanisms was identified using scaling analysis
